<br />\n全港滿警察  椒氣未停<br />\n圍捕你多黑暗 不准發聲<br />\n六點半新聞  繼續維穩<br />\n這政府多可惡 漠視民情<br />\n<br />\n願香港可以 不再愁眉<br />\n同路有吉星照 百事無忌<br />\n共相約煲底 脫下頭盔<br />\n吸下新鮮空氣 歡暢揚眉<br />\n<br />\n防暴到 防暴到 街坊好苦惱<br />\n防暴話 防暴話 採訪須申報<br />\n防暴到 防暴到 好走快兩步<br />\n一陣佢兇鳩你 你變暴徒<br />\n<br />\n啦啦啦啦啦啦 走到好走啦<br />\n啦啦啦啦啦啦 不必死守啦<br />\n防暴到 防暴到 好走快兩步<br />\n一俾佢捉到你 你變暴徒<br />\n<br />\n若果有撕紙 必冇運行（冇運行）<br />\n還望各位書友 百業成就（有成就）<br />\n日子再艱苦 抗共同舟（共同舟）<br />\n光復香港好嗎 享受自由<br />\n<br />\n 大眾慶香港 革命成功</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:30:10.000Z","msg":"一俾佢睇到你  你要潛逃<br />\n一俾佢睇到你  即刻拘捕"},{"pid":"40513466825774e08f39182a02ad2fcbd20b2ddd","tid":1833963,"uid":285120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:30:20.000Z","msg":"正~~~~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3603251379ed9d461bcfdddd7309914a1f5244c","tid":1833963,"uid":26703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c11fe82f8be31866737eeea10b6d5ebb6d3696","tid":1833963,"uid":330509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:30:39.000Z","msg":"巧巧聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b669acdd96f111d5c71e3cc1eb61f4fcdbd5a2","tid":1833963,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:32:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b85e318df8ee7b9288ab04cc5abd66d9747044fb","tid":1833963,"uid":61445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:34:50.000Z","msg":"good"},{"pid":"8dd10efb0ada2a86929c90e9bc71b8c6d11b0336","tid":1833963,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:35:09.0